      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "读写部分再细化一下：ARB_READ授权后进入READ，READ完成再到ARB_WRITE，然后授权进入WRITE。最后WRITE完成要有个CHAIN状态来处理多页链式请求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARB_READ",
        "READ",
        "ARB_WRITE",
        "WRITE",
        "CHAIN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "CHAIN有两个出口对吧？如果不是最后一页就Next回到FETCH继续，是最后一页就到COMPLETE结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CHAIN",
        "FETCH",
